lass=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617042\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617042\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xtb1665702702029.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xtb1665702702029.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xtb1665702702029.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xtb1665702702029\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Relationship\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Relationship is a Development Object that represents an association between one entity and another. It specifies the primary or candidate keys to be used in maintaining the association, as well as the delete constraints to be used when deleting occurrences in the related entities.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__section_w166ab1b5b1_w167ab1b5_w168ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__section_w169ab1b5b3_w170ab1b5_w171ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1003317e56\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">rel</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tza1665702561698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tza1665702561698.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity is an Entity that defines a logical data aggregation at an abstract level. It is used to model the default properties and code of an entity, so that the Entity can be referenced and inherited by derived entities in components.\">Modeled Entity</a> (<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"chf1665702702105.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/chf1665702702105.html\" title=\"A Many Entity is a Modeled Entity that represents the many side in a one-to-many relationship. It has foreign key fields that match the Primary Key of the One Entity.\">Many Entity</a>),\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnq1665702702174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnq1665702702174.html\" title=\"A Subtype Entity specializes a Modeled Entity (also known as the Supertype Entity). It is used to define a data set (or subset) for a special purpose, but that can be stored in the same database table as its Supertype.\">Subtype Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xtb1665702702029__table_d10535e1_d10536e1_d10537e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModeledEntityName</var>/rel:<var class=\"keyword varname\">RelationshipName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__section_w172ab1b5b5_w173ab1b5_w174ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1003317e260\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95204e1_d95205e1_d95206e1\">Relationship specializes Development Object in the\n            following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37484e1_d37485e1_d37486e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95207e1_d95208e1_d95209e1\">It has a Many Entity as the parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37487e1_d37488e1_d37489e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95210e1_d95211e1_d95212e1\">If has no child development objects or code\n                  containers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95213e1_d95214e1_d95215e1\">A Relationship is always one-to-many and belongs to\n            the Many Entity. Occurrence constraints can be used to specify a one-to-one\n            relationship. Many-to-many relationships must be implemented by using an intermediate\n            entity.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__section_w175ab1b5b7_w176ab1b5_w177ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1003317e287\"> Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95219e1_d95220e1_d95221e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37490e1_d37491e1_d37492e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37493e1_d37494e1_d37495e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37496e1_d37497e1_d37498e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37499e1_d37500e1_d37501e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37502e1_d37503e1_d37504e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95222e1_d95223e1_d95224e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37505e1_d37506e1_d37507e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gxv1665702701743.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gxv1665702701743.html\" title=\"Ordered list of fields comprising the specified Key of a Modeled Entity.\">Key Fields</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__p_d95225e1_d95226e1_d95227e1\">Behavior Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37508e1_d37509e1_d37510e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nbo1665702702246.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbo1665702702246.html\" title=\"Defines Uniface behavior when an occurrence of the One Entity is deleted, and there are related occurrences of the many entity available in the component data structure. Valid values are Restricted (default), Cascading, or Nullify.\">Delete Constraint</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37511e1_d37512e1_d37513e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"osh1665702702318.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/osh1665702702318.html\" title=\"Determines whether an index for the foreign key is maintained by the DBMS. Valid values are Y or N (default).\">Index on Foreign Key</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37514e1_d37515e1_d37516e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"son1665702702388.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/son1665702702388.html\" title=\"Determines whether referential integrity should be maintained in the database (rather than by Uniface). Valid values are T or F (default).\">Referential Integrity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xtb1665702702029__li_d37517e1_d37518e1_d37519e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwd1665702702457.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwd1665702702457.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of a script or stored procedure that is called to enforce referential integrity for this relationship if the database is made responsible for managing referential integrity.\">Procedure</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617042\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617042\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Relationship Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Relationship A Relationship is a Development Object that represents an association between one entity and another. It specifies the primary or candidate keys to be used in maintaining the association, as well as the delete constraints to be used when deleting occurrences in the related entities. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: rel Main Development Object? No Part of: Modeled Entity ( Many Entity ), Subtype Entity Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: ent: ModeledEntityName /rel: RelationshipName Specialization Relationship specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Many Entity as the parent. If has no child development objects or code containers. A Relationship is always one-to-many and belongs to the Many Entity. Occurrence constraints can be used to specify a one-to-one relationship. Many-to-many relationships must be implemented by using an intermediate entity. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Configuration Properties: Key Fields Behavior Properties: Delete Constraint Index on Foreign Key Referential Integrity Procedure Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}